name: The Maxine Print
description:
Limited run of the 'Maxine' print. 

Handcrafted artwork using watercolour, ink and sketching with digital colouring. Giclee printing on Hahnemuhle Torchon - a bright white, 100% α-cellulose paper – guarantees archival standards. 

This watercolour paper features a distinct textured surface. Acid free, Calcium Carbonate buffered, 285gsm.

10" x 13" & 16" x 20" size prints are made to order, usually shipped within 7 - 10 business days.

Custom sizing available on request.

** All artwork remains copyright of Annie Everingham and must not be reproduced in any way.
